      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="WndManager-cpp"><a href="#WndManager-cpp" class="headerlink" title="WndManager.cpp"></a>WndManager.cpp</h1><h2 id="1"><a href="#1" class="headerlink" title="1"></a>1</h2><p>搜索字段:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">nAddedOptDST[0] = DST_HP_MAX;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
