      <title>骑士双手武器携带盾牌</title>
      <link>http://nai-8.com/2017/04/19/%E9%AA%91%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E6%90%BA%E5%B8%A6%E7%9B%BE%E7%89%8C/</link>
      <guid>http://nai-8.com/2017/04/19/%E9%AA%91%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E6%90%BA%E5%B8%A6%E7%9B%BE%E7%89%8C/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Apr 2017 16:26:30 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h1 id=&quot;第一部分&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#第一部分&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;第一部分&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;第一部分&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;MoverEquip.cpp中搜索字段&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;
      
      </description>
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="第一部分"><a href="#第一部分" class="headerlink" title="第一部分"></a>第一部分</h1><p>MoverEquip.cpp中搜索字段<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>( pItemProp-&gt;dwItemKind3 == IK3_SHIELD )</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如下:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">// 炼扒八荤.</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>( pItemProp-&gt;dwItemKind3 == IK3_SHIELD )	// 规菩幅甫 馒侩窍妨 沁阑锭</div><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>( pHandItemProp &amp;&amp; pHandItemProp-&gt;dwHanded == HD_TWO )		// 颊俊 零绊 乐绰霸 捧勤靛搁.</div><div class="line">	&#123;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span>( pInventory )</div><div class="line">		&#123;</div><div class="line">			CItemElem *pItemElemOld = pInventory-&gt;GetEquip( PARTS_RWEAPON );</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span>( pInventory-&gt;UnEquip( PARTS_RWEAPON ) == FALSE )	</div><div class="line">				<span class="built_in">return</span> FALSE;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>插入:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_MASTER &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_HERO &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_LORDTEMPLER_HERO )</div><div class="line">&#123;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>修改为:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">// 炼扒八荤.</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>( pItemProp-&gt;dwItemKind3 == IK3_SHIELD )	// 规菩幅甫 馒侩窍妨 沁阑锭</div><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>(pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_MASTER &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_HERO &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_LORDTEMPLER_HERO )</div><div class="line">	&#123;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span>( pHandItemProp &amp;&amp; pHandItemProp-&gt;dwHanded == HD_TWO )		// 颊俊 零绊 乐绰霸 捧勤靛搁.</div><div class="line">		&#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span>( pInventory )</div><div class="line">			&#123;</div><div class="line">				CItemElem *pItemElemOld = pInventory-&gt;GetEquip( PARTS_RWEAPON );</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span>( pInventory-&gt;UnEquip( PARTS_RWEAPON ) == FALSE )	</div><div class="line">					<span class="built_in">return</span> FALSE;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="第二部分"><a href="#第二部分" class="headerlink" title="第二部分"></a>第二部分</h1><p>如果你想让其他职业有双手武器的可以带上盾牌,需要修改<br>As you may notice i defined it in the versioncommon.h of the neuz and worldserver<br>as this</p>
<p>#define __2HANDED_SHIELD</p>
<p>Now if you want to let Jesters/Ringmaster and or every other class that wears an 2 handed weapon also be aible to wear an shield then the only thing you have to change is this line</p>
<p>if(pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_MASTER &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_KNIGHT_HERO &amp;&amp; pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_LORDTEMPLER_HERO )</p>
<p>You need then to enter more jobs for it. Remember to do it like this</p>
<p>pMover-&gt;GetJob() != JOB_RINGMASTER &lt;– see this ( != ) that means if its not the same.</p>
<p>Now after you have changed it rebuild the neuz and the worldserver to let it work.</p>
<p>There have fun with it.</p>
<p>摘自国外论坛,最后一句自行理解,博主也没搞懂 : (</p>
<p>发现问题可以留言.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      
